snippet.title: Dwarf Fortress Steam Edition - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Strike the Earth! Dwarf Fortress Steam Edition releases December 6th, 2022 on Steam and itch.io. Buy now on Steam: https://bit.ly/2PY0P0w

➫Join the Official Dwarf Fortress Discord: https://bit.ly/3W1HvfX
➫Sign up for Dwarf Mail: https://bit.ly/3uYfudW

Song: Koganusan - Simon Swerwer
